Class GameOverController

  • java.lang.Object
    • GameOverController

  • public class GameOverController
extends java.lang.Object
    This class gives you three options when the game gets over 1. New Game: Helps user to again select number of players and grid size and start a new game 2. Restart: Restarts the game just played 3. Quit: Quits the game
